T1  - Resource Allocation to Interrelated Risky Projects Using a Multiattribute Utility Function
AU  - Mehrez, Abraham
AU  - Sinuany-Stern, Zilla
Y1  - 1983/04/01
PY  - 1983
DA  - 1983/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.29.4.430
